    <item>
      <title>维旺迪的 Canal+ 股份触发 MultiChoice 的强制要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/vivendi-s-canal-stake-triggers-mandatory-offer-for-multichoice</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据南非收购监管小组的裁决，在 MultiChoice Group 将其在非洲付费电视业务的持股比例增至 35% 以上后，Vivendi SE 旗下 Canal+ 必须向 MultiChoice Group 提出强制收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/vivendi-s-canal-stake-triggers-mandatory-offer-for-multichoice</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
